Dear Dr. Foaad Khosmood,



Greetings!



I would like to take the liberty of contacting you regarding manuscript
submission. I have gone through your recently published article and found
that your research fits to our journal. It would be great if you could share
the possible submissions with us for upcoming issue of the journal.



We follow a fast track peer-review and publication process, which takes only
2-3 weeks from the date of submission to publish the article.



Upon your research Interest you can submit your paper towards any of our
journal: Annals of Heart | ISSN: 2578-6520 and Journal of Cardiothoracic
Surgery and Therapeutics | ISSN: 2643-5780.




Submission Process


Submission process can be initiated via our user-friendly online submission
system
<https://scholarlypages.org/submit-manuscript.php?journal=cardiothoracic-sur
gery>  or you can send as an attachment to this mail.





Due Date


Submission due date October 20, 2019. If you have a manuscript ready for
publication you can submit immediately.

I hope you are able to accept this request. Please do not hesitate to
contact us for any assistance.



Awaiting your positive response.



Yours sincerely,



Managing Editor

Scholarly Pages

1805 N Carson Street, Suite S

Carson City, Nevada 89701, USA



As an international peer reviewed journal, we try to provide up to date
information to cardiologists with important research advances in
cardiovascular disease.



Note: If you do not wish to receive our emails, you can opt out by sending a
reply email with subject "UNSUBSCRIBE" and we assure you will not receive
any of our mails.

